  ('generalpolice-3218f787-moex-00168', 'generalpolice-3218f787', 'generalpolice-3218f787-moex-113-7ac5ce32', 'sub-generalpolice-3218f787-05', NULL, 'essay', '臺灣社會變遷快速，社會價值多元化，犯罪行為事件亦迅速增加。請說
